profile:
Ascent Yard Care provides arborist and garden services to Greater Victoria and beyond. Our dedicated team is proud to provide comprehensive service from start to finish.

Each customer receives a free in-person assessment and quote by Jake, owner and arborist. We take the time to understand our customers' needs so we can provide the best and most effective service for every situation.

Fast Service. Free Quotes. Since 2017.
